  "id": "camp_leader",
  "nodes": {
    "start": {
      "speaker": "Marda, Camp Leader",
      "text": "New blood. The Vale takes everyone the same and keeps them different. Rule here is simple: you're worth what you can do. So — what are you worth?",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "I broke the east shaft's jammed lift cage with my hands. Ore's moving again.",
          "requires": {
            "quest_active": [
              "earn_your_place"
            ],
            "attributes": {
              "might": 1
            }
          },
          "show_locked": true,
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "apply_approach",
              "attribute": "might"
            },
            {
              "type": "complete_quest",
              "quest": "earn_your_place",
              "approach": "might"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "camp_member"
            },
            {
              "type": "start_quest",
              "quest": "free_the_prisoner"
            },
            {
              "type": "journal",
              "text": "Marda watched you bend the lift cage back into true. You eat with the diggers now."
            }
          ],
          "next": "accepted"
        },
        {
          "text": "Your quartermaster skims a tenth of every ration crate. I can prove it — or keep proving useful.",
          "requires": {
            "quest_active": [
              "earn_your_place"
            ],
            "attributes": {
              "guile": 1
            }
          },
          "show_locked": true,
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "apply_approach",
              "attribute": "guile"
            },
            {
              "type": "complete_quest",
              "quest": "earn_your_place",
              "approach": "guile"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "camp_member"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "knows_quartermaster_secret"
            },
            {
              "type": "start_quest",
              "quest": "free_the_prisoner"
            },
            {
              "type": "journal",
              "text": "Marda didn't thank you for the tip about the quartermaster. She promoted you instead."
            }
          ],
          "next": "accepted"
        },
        {
          "text": "Your smelter burns wrong. Blue flame means the flux is contaminated — I can fix the mix.",
          "requires": {
            "quest_active": [
              "earn_your_place"
            ],
            "attributes": {
              "lore": 1
            }
          },
          "show_locked": true,
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "apply_approach",
              "attribute": "lore"
            },
            {
              "type": "complete_quest",
              "quest": "earn_your_place",
              "approach": "lore"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "camp_member"
            },
            {
              "type": "start_quest",
              "quest": "free_the_prisoner"
            },
            {
              "type": "journal",
              "text": "The smelter runs clean for the first time in a season. Marda called you 'scholar' and it wasn't quite mockery."
            }
          ],
          "next": "accepted"
        },
        {
          "text": "The diggers haven't sung since the cave-in. I sat with them last night. They'll work tomorrow.",
          "requires": {
            "quest_active": [
              "earn_your_place"
            ],
            "attributes": {
              "heart": 1
            }
          },
          "show_locked": true,
          "effects": [
            {
              "type": "apply_approach",
              "attribute": "heart"
            },
            {
              "type": "complete_quest",
              "quest": "earn_your_place",
              "approach": "heart"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "camp_member"
            },
            {
              "type": "set_flag",
              "flag": "diggers_trust_you"
            },
            {
              "type": "start_quest",
              "quest": "free_the_prisoner"
            },
            {
              "type": "journal",
              "text": "Marda says morale isn't her department. She also stopped posting a guard on your tent."
            }
          ],
          "next": "accepted"
        },
        {
          "text": "What happens to people who aren't worth anything?",
          "effects": [],
          "next": "worth_nothing"
        },
        {
          "text": "[Leave]",
          "effects": [],
          "next": ""
        }
      ]
